<view class="page settings-page">
  <view class="safe-head"></view><view class="eyebrow">PREFERENSI</view><view class="title">学习设置</view>
  <view class="profile card"><view class="avatar">B</view><view class="profile-copy"><view>Bahasa Learner</view><text>正在建立印尼语思维</text></view><view class="profile-mark">PRO</view></view>
  <view class="group-title">每日计划</view>
  <view class="setting-card card">
    <view class="setting-row"><view class="setting-icon green">Aa</view><view class="setting-copy"><view>每日新词</view><text>建议 10–20 个，轻松坚持</text></view><view class="stepper"><button data-key="daily_new_words" data-delta="-5" bindtap="step">−</button><text>{{daily_new_words}}</text><button data-key="daily_new_words" data-delta="5" bindtap="step">＋</button></view></view>
    <view class="line"></view>
    <view class="setting-row"><view class="setting-icon coral">↻</view><view class="setting-copy"><view>复习上限</view><text>控制每天的复习量</text></view><view class="stepper"><button data-key="daily_review_limit" data-delta="-10" bindtap="step">−</button><text>{{daily_review_limit}}</text><button data-key="daily_review_limit" data-delta="10" bindtap="step">＋</button></view></view>
  </view>
  <view class="group-title">数据连接</view>
  <view class="server card"><view class="server-head"><view><view>SQLite 学习服务</view><text>小程序通过此地址访问本地词库</text></view><view class="online"></view></view><input value="{{apiBase}}" bindinput="onAddress" placeholder="http://192.168.x.x:3000"/></view>
  <view class="notice"><text>i</text><view>真机测试时不能填写 localhost，请填写电脑的局域网 IP；发布时需要配置已备案的 HTTPS 域名。</view></view>
  <button class="primary-button save" loading="{{saving}}" bindtap="save">保存并测试连接</button>
  <view class="version">BahasaBelajar · 小程序版 2.0</view>
</view>
